{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He, he would-- and we had to sort of tie ourselves onto the bed, because when you put a bed up, first of all, you have to lie upside down, because if you lay down like that, you'd be down with your head backwards.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we tried to do it the other way, where we would be in a standing position when he folded it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept sinking down into the blankets and nearly smothering.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother said, impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll pull this bed down any minute, first thing when they come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it looked like a cupboard, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he had thought that was not a bad idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was no good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he realized that I had to have something done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is really where he found somebody who was hiding children, who was putting children in hiding places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so one morning, he sat me down-- one evening, actually, it was-- and he said, look, Corrie, we have to do something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's getting too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All our family's being raided, and they've been sent to concentration camps, and they-- at that stage, they thought they were work camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody thought they were going still to work camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They hadn't come to the conclusion that these were actually concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They thought it was work for the people, and they would come back after two months, and everything would be wonderful.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was all marvelous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they decided then that this gentleman that had offered for my-- apparently, this is what happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My parents had got a hiding place of which they didn't want any children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They said it was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No children, and, you know, they, they just couldn't have it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
